data.name: UpdateDebtDetail
data.value: update CKT_DEBT_DTL set DUE_DT = @dueDt, BAL_DUE_AMT = @balDueAmt, INT_BAL_DUE_AMT = @intBalDueAmt, ADC_DT = @adcDt, RETIRED_DT = @retiredDt, CVRD_PRD_START_DT = @cvrdPrdStartDt, CVD_PRD_END_DT = @cvdPrdEndDt, PRECNVRSN_PGM_CD = @precnvrsnPgmCd, LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy where (OBG_GENERATED_ID = @obgGeneratedId) and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (OTR_GENERATED_ID = @otrGeneratedId) and (OTY_TYPE = @otyType) and (OTR_TYPE = @otrType)
